1.title: Dziki Mlyn
1.plot: Magda Gessler visit the first restaurant that is to undergo a revolution: a place called Dziki Mlyn in Warsaw. The owners seem to have no interest in running the restaurant and the manager tries to please everyone.

2.title: Panorama
2.plot: Magda Gessler goes to Gdansk, where at the highest floor of a skyscraper a restaurant called Panorama is located. The location is beautiful, but the owners are too young and inexperienced to make the restaurant work properly.

3.title: Franc Josef
3.plot: Magda Gessler goes to Katowice to help a restaurant Franc Josef. The food is very good, but the stuff is unmotivated ans some of them drink alcohol during work hours.
